Package com.dkriesel.snipe.util

Contains some SNIPE utilities: A random number generator (which is not mine; see its class documentation for copyright information) and a class which generates DOT-Code of a neural net in order to visualize a neural net using GraphViz.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
GraphVizEncoder Experimental tool that returns some designed code for the GraphViz DOT Engine (see graphviz.org) to visualize the neural net.
MersenneTwisterFast MersenneTwister and MersenneTwisterFast Version 16, based on version MT199937(99/10/29) of the Mersenne Twister algorithm found at The Mersenne Twister Home Page, with the initialization improved using the new 2002/1/26 initialization algorithm By Sean Luke, October 2004.
 

Package com.dkriesel.snipe.util Description

Contains some SNIPE utilities: A random number generator (which is not mine; see its class documentation for copyright information) and a class which generates DOT-Code of a neural net in order to visualize a neural net using GraphViz.
